  "description": "The ***Paramedic Method*** is a step-by-step procedure for revising wordy, nominalized prose, developed by [Richard Lanham](../../../../../../../references/people/richard-lanham.md) in *Revising Prose* [@lanham2006]. It treats [revision](../../essay-writing/terms/revision.md) as a learnable, repeatable skill rather than an intuitive art.",
